{"tid":2086653,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃圈黃店指不批評退出黃色經濟圈嘅店","createTime":"2020-06-30T10:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T12:52:18.000Z","uid":145118,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"51a26f53d9fcb9f7ce7c2ef58d136dfda31d8bce","tid":2086653,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:59:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/977NFxh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F977NFxh.png&h=68f7ac03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打還是巴打唔批評人地，亦唔比意見，<br />\n<br />\n都年幾啦，<br />\n同我隻豬一樣傷既傷，<br />\n坐既坐，死既死，走既走流亡既流亡。<br />\n你問我驚唔驚<br />\n驚點解唔驚<br />\n有兒有女<br />\n佢就係想你驚<br />\n當全部人一齊唔驚佢就驚架啦<br />\n係咪咁講先不割口號黎咩？<br />\n得個嗌字？<br />\n問下自己點解當日行出黎好有？<br />\n<br />\n生於亂世有種責任<br />\n不忘初衷<br />\n寧化飛灰不作浮孚塵<br />\n可能係最後一個post<br />\n71見<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=679566292892716&amp;id=278840489631967\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D679566292892716%26id%3D278840489631967&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F5hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=69771907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=679566292892716&amp;id=278840489631967</a><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈唔會係收皮！<br />\n今日可能國安法殺到埋嚟<br />\n但未必會令整個運動全滅<br />\n因為我哋仲面對緊呢個社會嘅不公義<br />\n我哋係無可能因為國安法而放棄<br />\n無可能放棄所有反送中被控暴動嘅人<br />\n<br />\n法律從來管唔到人<br />\n係人先可以改變呢個社會<br />\n<br />\n法律<br />\n係死<br />\n<br />\n人係生<br />\n只要一啖氣<br />\n都要抗爭到底<br />\n<br />\n只要呢個政權仲係衰<br />\n點都會有一個人出嚟發聲<br />\n有第一個就有第二個人<br />\n612當時都係咁嚟發生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各有各做<br />\n勿負面影響"},{"pid":"399d126b036e693078f562d59210c64da641f727","tid":2086653,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ukJEwH6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FukJEwH6.jpg&h=9d7e8335&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2b194fcfe264535e66d0d913646f23cd7da1973","tid":2086653,"uid":145118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ppWKHPV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FppWKHPV.jpg&h=d4d9aa52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec82c29aa1ac314e5f5ee9225f6464e390934daf","tid":2086653,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QdafPu3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQdafPu3.jpg&h=220406ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2b65305a6b2905ca7c542abb630c7fac696c984","tid":2086653,"uid":282352,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:07:53.000Z","msg":"賺夠fatfat 就離場 ,對得住手足？<br />\n一句有後果就唔做,咁手足一直做緊咩？<br />\n唔係一直話違法達義咩？<br />\n不過連登仔都會話核彈都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過人地割你啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08b4b459f9e5f63880af86dc6c6b9fbf5988097","tid":2086653,"uid":286630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"G持！"},{"pid":"737546fdedbd97f59334c0f326ffdc1bda2377a5","tid":2086653,"uid":145118,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:13:31.000Z","msg":"我撐仲抗爭緊嘅黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會嘈一啲無幫助抗爭嘅嘢<br />\n我出呢個post係帶出一啲正面嘅訊息"},{"pid":"751bbd17144bdb7163d670dc0d832f92a8109b00","tid":2086653,"uid":2397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"批鬥黃店果班一係假膠一係5毛 今日請大家集中返71<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2086563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2086563</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7ab3e7e949d2cde235496e626f236305658f3325","tid":2086653,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8tAzkGk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8tAzkGk.png&h=63df2c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gk8X2UG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGk8X2UG.png&h=42ae6559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我建議你講少啲無謂嘢說話"},{"pid":"c3d7e72fd13030d5563dcfeebb92b43d195750c6","tid":2086653,"uid":20459,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:18:25.000Z","msg":"黃店都係為賺錢 國安殺到黎仲唔退咩<br />\n睇下其他鋪頭呢兩日點樣 係咪拆晒d文宣"},{"pid":"2f36cd3d5a8c2925bbf85e982bbe4ca3967942d0","tid":2086653,"uid":145118,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f2b65305a6b2905ca7c542abb630c7fac696c984","tid":2086653,"uid":282352,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:07:53.000Z","msg":"賺夠fatfat 就離場 ,對得住手足？<br />\n一句有後果就唔做,咁手足一直做緊咩？<br />\n唔係一直話違法達義咩？<br />\n不過連登仔都會話核彈都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過人地割你啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不同意<br />\n<br />\n從來黃色經濟圈係for一啲唔幫襯鄉黑/紅底嘅同路人<br />\n有個別嘅黃店有捐錢同支援<br />\n所以本身就唔係間間都咁有心<br />\n<br />\n唔排除係被自己人屌到退出，手足被人當鬼都會話退出啦！所以呢點無乜好鬧。<br />\n<br />\n只能講唔係間間退出咗黃圈嘅黃店都係敢於冒險，唔係人人都承受到政權嘅打壓同清算。<br />\n<br />\n割唔割都好個人，可能未必關係到連登呢堆人，唔係個個同路人都限於連登。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n71上街"},{"pid":"350acc01c353d112849ec46630eab11aa8cd3a05","tid":2086653,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3d7e72fd13030d5563dcfeebb92b43d195750c6","tid":2086653,"uid":20459,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:18:25.000Z","msg":"黃店都係為賺錢 國安殺到黎仲唔退咩<br />\n睇下其他鋪頭呢兩日點樣 係咪拆晒d文宣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:23:31.000Z","msg":"睇你點睇黃店嘅個存在<br />\n將金錢價值觀擺係第一位<br />\n固定覺得黃店係無良商店"},{"pid":"5d03c8a349da824fa748224d